      <div class="card"><h3>Medium Walk-In (10–25 m²)</h3><p>For large bakeries and restaurants with substantial cold storage needs. Includes shelving and lighting.</p><div class="price-tag">₹5,00,000 – ₹10,00,000</div></div>
